@startuml
title
<size:16><b>UC-09: Process Payment - Activity Diagram</b></size>
end title

|Buyer|
start

:Presented with Payment Gateway page showing order total in LKR;

:Select payment method (Credit/Debit Card, Bank Transfer, Mobile Wallet);

:Enter payment credentials;

|Payment Gateway|
:Process the transaction;

if (Transaction approved?) then (no)
  :Send failure webhook to SmartTech;
  |System|
  :Receive webhook, verify signature;
  :Update Order status to 'Payment Failed';
  |Buyer|
  :Redirected to Payment Failed page with option to retry;
  note right: Alternative Flow 1
  stop
else (yes)
endif

:Send success webhook to SmartTech;

|System|
:Receive webhook, verify signature (BR-16);

:Update Order status to 'Confirmed';

:Update Buyer payment record (immutable - BR-17);

|Buyer|
:Redirected to Order Confirmation page;

stop
@enduml